Speak to a Black Lion Armor Trader at the trading post in any major city to exchange this item for an outfit wearable in combat.

Become a wisp of natural energy, traversing to the targeted location. When you reach the target, heal nearby allies and grant protection to your pet. Recharge is reduced if you heal another ally.

This finisher is awarded to accounts that have turned in enough Order of Shadow Seals.

Plant 3 Fire Orchid Seeds at the Cathedral of Verdance in Cursed Shore.
Throw out the contents, preferably far from the palace.

Edge of the Mists provides instant access to competitive play and can be enjoyed while you're waiting for a Mist War map.<brx>Progress made in the Edge of the Mists does not count toward the Mist War score.<brx>Victory in the Edge of the Mists provides a supply drop to the citadel in your Borderlands map.

When you gain a boon, it is shared with your pet.

Can be consumed for unbound magic or traded with vendors.
Bring a Fire Orchid to Broadleaf on a ledge above the Savage Rise.
Raze the area around you with Sohothin's fury.
You must own the Triumphant Shoulderguards skin before you can purchase this armor.

Double-click to convert 50 Shards of Glory into loot bags. The converter can be used five times a day.
